                  </hi>. Aged 25.—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18450818-1641-punishment-51" type="punishmentDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18450818-1641-punishment-51" type="punishmentCategory" value="transport"></interp>
                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1641-18450818 t18450818-1641-punishment-51"></join>Transported for Seven Years</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
